com.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.strategy

Class StrategyWrappedGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.strategy.StrategyWrappedGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph, StrategyWrapped, com.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.util.wrapped.WrappedGraph<Graph>, AutoCloseable

    public class StrategyWrappedGraph
extends Object
implements Graph, StrategyWrapped, com.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.util.wrapped.WrappedGraph<Graph>
    A wrapper class for Graph instances that host and apply a GraphStrategy. The wrapper implements Graph itself and intercepts calls made to the hosted instance and then applies the strategy. Methods that return an extension of Element or a Property will be automatically wrapped in a StrategyWrapped implementation.
    Author:
    Stephen Mallette (http://stephen.genoprime.com)
